title: july 22: supergirl (with Nari)
description:
In this episode of 365 days with mxmtoon, Maia talks about the first casting of a transgender superhero in “Supergirl”. After, she’s joined by musical guest Nari. Listen to this episode today and make sure you’re following along with the daily updates @365daysmxmtoon on all platforms.
